description: Dashboard for monitoring individual SFS Client RPC nodes performance and operations

targets.expr: rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )
targets.query: rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )

targets.expr: (rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))
targets.query: (rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))

targets.expr: rate( sfs_rpc_request_size_bytes_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node",method="READ"} [$__rate_interval] )
targets.query: rate( sfs_rpc_request_size_bytes_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node",method="READ"} [$__rate_interval] )

targets.expr: rate( sfs_rpc_request_size_bytes_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node",method="WRITE"} [$__rate_interval] )
targets.query: rate( sfs_rpc_request_size_bytes_sum {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node",method="WRITE"} [$__rate_interval] )

targets.expr: sum( sfs_rpc_inflight_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} )
targets.query: sum( sfs_rpc_inflight_count {cluster="$cluster",job="sfs-client",rpc_nsid="$nsid",instance="$node"} )

targets.expr: histogram_quantile(0.01, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))
targets.query: histogram_quantile(0.01, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))

targets.expr: histogram_quantile(0.9, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))
targets.query: histogram_quantile(0.9, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))

targets.expr: histogram_quantile(0.5, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))
targets.query: histogram_quantile(0.5, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))

targets.expr: histogram_quantile(0.95, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))
targets.query: histogram_quantile(0.95, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", rpc_nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))
